details.name: Street Race - High Society
details.creator: RSI_sidhant
details.desc: The community council of Rockford Hills have issued a formal complaint over the reckless racing in their good, god-fearing American streets. There's only one rational response. Settle into the power-slide, pull down your pants, and drop a fat deuce out of the window as you pass the AGM. Lap race for Los Santos Tuners.
